  <description type="morphology">Plants (4–)6–8(–10.5) cm. Secondary stem leaves 2–3.2 × 1–1.7 mm. Branch leaves oblong-ovate to ovate, 1–2.2 × 0.5–0.8 mm; margins serrate at apex; apex obtuse to broadly acute; basal laminal cells 5–8 × 1–2 µm; medial juxtacostal cells long-rhomboidal, longest axis parallel to costa, 3–5 × 1–3 µm; apical cells subquadrate to short-rhomboidal, 2–4 × 1–2 µm. Sexual condition dioicous.</description>
